label: content
definition: A single physical entity inhering in an bearer by virtue of the bearer's quantities or qualities.

label: gross
definition: Gains prior to deduction of losses; pre-deducted value (gross), post-deducted value (net).

label: abundance
definition: The degree of quantity of an entity.

label: median
comment: In STATO has a different name: center value

label: standard error
comment: In STATO has a different name: standard error of the mean
